\cf2 \strokec3 4.Selezionare tutti gli studenti con i dati relativi al corso di laurea a cui sono iscritti e il\strokec2  \strokec3 relativo dipartimento, in ordine alfabetico per cognome e nome\cf3 \
\
SELECT `students`.`id`, `students`.`name` AS `nome`, `students`.`surname` AS `cognome`, `students`.`registration_number` AS `n_matricola`,`degrees`.`name` AS `corso_di_laurea`, `departments`.`name` AS `dipartimento`\
FROM `students`\
JOIN `degrees` ON `degrees`.`id`=`students`.`degree_id`\
JOIN `departments` ON `departments`.`id`=`degrees`.`department_id`\
ORDER BY `students`.`surname`, `students`.`name`\
;\
